author: Nostalgia Nerd
description:
Well folks, it's here, The brand new Commodore 64 Ultimate, or C64U as it's known. Bursting out of the newly formed Commodore International, this reinvigorated C64 has some serious tricks. Let's take a look, in this C64 Ultimate Review.

⌚Timings⌚
00:00-04:19 Introduction
04:19-12:14 Familiarising
12:14-16:17 Software & Peripherals
16:17-19:29 Hardware
19:29-22:42 The Important Tests
22:42-24:28 The Future we were Promised?
24:28-24:55 Credits
